Various experiments and work in progress.

	=== Xtreams.Log ===

This is really a development tool. It is for logging debugging information. It is used in some test suites (e.g. TLS or SSH) to log announcements from their connections. It should be initialized to a character write stream or 'nil writing' for logical off mode.
{{{
	Xtreams.Log := Stdout writing encoding: #ascii
}}}
